The Glenn Beck Program - 10/16/13


Wednesday, October 16, 2013 10:30 AM



Glenn describes our system of government as a thugocracy,
 there is no more democracy.
  Also, a communist is about to win the NYC mayoral race and no one seem's to care.
  Bill Deblasio is up in the polls and it's looking like he will be mayor of the most
  heavily populated city in America.

  Plus, journalist, author and Chief National Correspondent for The New York Times Magazine,
  John Leibovich, joins the show to discuss his latest book, The Town.
